==English==
===Alternative forms===
* {{l|en|Jeshua}}
===Etymology===
From {{der|en|hbo|יֵשׁוּעַ|tr=Yēšū́a|t=Jesus” ''or'' “Joshua}}. Cognate directly equivalent to {{m|en|Jesus}} via {{cog|la|Iēsus}} and {{cog|grc|Ἰησοῦς}} from nearly identical {{cog|arc|יֵשׁוּע|tr=Yēšū́ʿ}}. Cognate to {{m|en|Joshua}} from related variant Hebrew form {{m|he|יְהוֹשֻׁעַ|tr=Yĕhōšúa|t=Joshua}}.
